{"tid":497550,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[正能量] 俾人狙擊有感","createTime":"2017-12-13T01:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T04:38:16.000Z","uid":8260,"like":1,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f978c13ae737279bd37cfb7606061fafbf9b11","tid":497550,"uid":8260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:33:04.000Z","msg":"近排有個/有班傻鳩係咁狙擊我, 好在本身我個人都無乜所謂唔記仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當睇馬騮戲咁<br />\n不過小弟發現原來俾人狙擊都幾好, 又多咗follower, 又有人問我發生咩事, 同佢地嘅互動又多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然我唔知你係邊個, 但都估到係邊個圈子嘅人喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  請你繼續開post 留言狙擊我, 我大方<br />\n<br />\n如果大家唔識我, 歡迎follow 我ig, 喺呢個post 留返低你ig, 我得閒會follow 返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/183.852/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F183.852%2F&d=DGK2LAqmCD1msRExv7znd26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b2939d28\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/183.852/</a><br />\n<br />\n嗱, 實有d 柒頭會話我自編自導自演<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 清者自清, 信不信由你喇, 一陣可能又多幾個分身叫 壹捌叁 一八三 之類, 到時真係要留名跟佢地學搞gag同狙擊人<br />\n<br />\n攝台一慣風氣, 大家俾個正負皮講下你嘅睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正評: 樓豬收皮啦<br />\n負皮: 撐!天地有正氣"},{"pid":"88e4cade83d911b9dcd2fdc84fb99ac84e4b98b1","tid":497550,"uid":8260,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:33:52.000Z","msg":"你改左呢兩張圖真係好好笑好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  thanks for sharing<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/xT0xeCHho18kxEEEOA/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FxT0xeCHho18kxEEEOA%2Fgiphy.gif&h=c94150b8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/